  Note                     = {{\bf Advanced Normalization Tools} (ANTs) implemented in C++ (ITK), works across species and organ systems: \\ \url{https://github.com/stnava/ANTs} \\ and interfaced to R: \\ \url{http://stnava.github.io/ANTsR} \,},
